{{Item infobox | description = Refine into [[Bloodstone Brick|bloodstone brick]]s. | type = crafting material | material type = ascended | tier = 7 | material storage = Ascended Materials | rarity = ascended | bound = account | id = 46731 }} [[Pile of Bloodstone Dust]] is a [[crafting material]] used in the process of [[crafting]] [[ascended]] gear.
== Acquisition == === Gathered from === {{gathered from}}
=== Contained in === ==== Guaranteed ==== {{contained in|columns=3|chance=Guaranteed}}
==== Chance ==== {{Contained in|columns=3|chance=Chance}}
=== Recipe === [[Bloodstone Brick]]s can be demoted through the [[Mystic Forge]]. {{recipe | source = Mystic Forge | quantity = 100 | type = Demotion | ingredient1 = 1 Bloodstone Brick | ingredient2 = 1 Pile of Bloodstone Dust | ingredient3 = 1 Fine Essence of Luck | ingredient4 = 1 Mystic Coin }}
=== Rewarded by === {{rewarded by}}
== Used in == {{recipe list by discipline}}
=== Other === * Completing [[The Bifrost I: The Experimental Staff]] collection requires 900 Piles of Bloodstone Dust.
== Currency for == {{see|Converter}} {{Vendor query table|currency=Pile of Bloodstone Dust}}
== Notes == * [[Seimur Oxbone]] is the only chef that uses bloodstone dust to make food.
== See also == * {{item icon|Dragonite Ore}} * {{item icon|Empyreal Fragment}}
[[de:Haufen Blutsteinstaub]] [[es:Montón de polvo de hematites]] [[fr:Tas de poussière de pierre de sang]]

{{Item infobox | type = Service | rarity = Rare | bound = Account | id = 75012 | requires = hot }} <small>As wallet currency:</small> {{Quotation|game|Earned and spent in Auric Basin. Train the Exalted Acceptance Mastery line to trade with Exalted merchants for auric weapon recipes and other goods.}} [[Lump of Aurillium]] is a [[currency]] earned by participating in events in [[Auric Basin]]. They are stored in the [[Currency|Account Wallet]] and can be spent at merchants within the Auric Basin.
== Acquisition == === Gathered from === {{gathered from}}
=== Contained in === {{contained in}}
=== Events === * Rewarded for completing [[:Category:Auric Basin events|events]] in [[Auric Basin]].
== Used in == {{recipe list}}
== Vendors == * The [[Priory Explorer (aurillium collector)|Aurillium Collector]] at the Pact Camp in [[Tarnished Treetop]] sells [[Exalted Key]]s and recipes for crafting Viper's prefix gear. * The [[Exalted Mastery Vendor]] in [[Tarir, the Forgotten City]] provides a wide variety of goods. * Used to purchase [[Machete]]s from the [[Whispers Keeper]] at the Pact Base Camp in [[Dragon's Stand]]. * Can be used in the appropriately upgraded [[Ley-Energy Matter Converter]] to purchase 1 container daily.
{{Currencies nav}}
[[de:Aurilliumklumpen]] [[es:Trozo de aurilio]] [[fr:Bloc d'aurillium]]
